data.title: Edward John Robeson Jr. (1890-1966) – Find a Grave...
data.meta_description: U.S. Congressman. Moving to Georgia, he graduated as a civil engineer from the University of Georgia in 1910 and worked in Ironwood, Michigan (1910 to 1915).
